<html>
<head>
    <style type="text/css" media="screen">
      table {
      	width: 100%;
      }
      td {
		color: gray;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: bold;
		vertical-align: baseline !important;
		}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

Come&Shop Order Shipped
This is just to let you know that we've shipped your recent order:

<table>
	<tr>
		<td>Qty</td>
		<td>Title</td>
		<td>Image</td>
		<td>Price</td>
	</tr>

	<% @order.line_items.each do |line_item| %>
	<tr>
		<td><%= line_item.quantity %></td>
		<td><%= line_item.product.title %></td>
		<td><%= image_tag (attachments["#{line_item.product.image_url}"].url), width:"50px%", height:"50px" %></td>
		<td class="item_price"><%=number_to_currency(line_item.total_price, :unit => "EGP ")%></td>
	</tr>
	<% end %>
</table>

</body>
</html>
